Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:36.00,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Dies
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.19,0:00:40.41,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Iræ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.55,0:00:44.67,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Dies
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.95,0:00:48.98,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Umbra
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.83,0:00:54.61,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,What is wrong, my subjects?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.98,0:00:58.50,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Is the moon not to your liking?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.02,0:01:01.03,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you just don’t see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.27,0:01:03.09,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The endless sea of black,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.52,0:01:07.17,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And all of the stars so striking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.69,0:01:09.61,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Do you dare to anger me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.75,0:01:11.30,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Is it so hard
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.62,0:01:14.72,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To give up the way things are?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.91,0:01:17.72,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Do you not see the wonders I create?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.42,0:01:20.06,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Why do you hide
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.30,0:01:23.48,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Away from the night and stars~?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.62,0:01:26.81,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Did I deserve your fear and hate~?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.14,0:01:28.27,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Well no more
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.45,0:01:30.52,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Usher the coming storm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.66,0:01:32.72,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Let darkness flood the morn
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.86,0:01:35.67,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And swallow every wayward light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.95,0:01:38.02,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Lay the seas and mountains
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.16,0:01:40.22,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Under blackened heavens
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.27,0:01:42.09,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Bow now citizens
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.23,0:01:44.62,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Unto the throne of night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.95,0:01:47.02,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Rise now regal~ moon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.16,0:01:53.25,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All the world consume
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.72,0:01:55.69,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Tremble at the sight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.87,0:01:58.03,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The eternal night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.17,0:01:60.00,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,What’s become of you sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.47,0:02:03.61,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Don’t you see your own soul wan~ing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.59,0:02:06.42,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,While this anger burns for me~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:08.44,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Please give me a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.14,0:02:12.23,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To save all that is remain~ing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.22,0:02:14.95,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And end this war I plea!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.14,0:02:16.31,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Stow your scorn
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.41,0:02:18.52,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Call off your hellish swarm
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.66,0:02:20.67,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Our people won’t be torn
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.81,0:02:23.72,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Because of your fiery spite
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.86,0:02:25.92,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Free them from your vengeance
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.11,0:02:28.17,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Or you’ll pay the penance
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.27,0:02:30.05,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Must you make me cast
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.19,0:02:32.62,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The sentence for this blight?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:35.44,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Dearest sister Luna
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.62,0:02:41.39,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,What have you~ done?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:44.25,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Can’t you see the monster
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.39,0:02:50.11,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You have be~come?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.27,0:03:54.14,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Sound the battle horn
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.28,0:03:56.30,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,As all the world will mourn
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.44,0:03:58.41,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,When family love’s forlorn
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:00.80,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,For warriors and might
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.84,0:04:02.81,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Beloved alicorns
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.95,0:04:05.02,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The angels we’d adorn
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.16,0:04:07.17,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,With majesty, will war
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:09.70,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And we will bear the plight
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.22,0:04:12.52,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,New allegiance will rise
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:18.05,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Thirsting for demise
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.75,0:04:21.09,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The winds will carry the ring
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.37,0:04:26.58,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Of walls crumbling
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.42,0:04:29.91,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The stage is set for the clash
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.14,0:04:35.25,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The magic is~ cast
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:39.98,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,As the battle begins